## Limitations

The findings are based on available online resources and may not encompass all perspectives or recent developments in the field. Additionally, the complexity of human behavior means that motivations for breaking the law can vary widely among individuals and cultures, which may not be fully captured in this report. Further research, including empirical studies and expert interviews, would provide a more nuanced understanding of this issue.